snippet.description:

A presentation by: Tej Narayan & Snehlatha Agarwal and I Am Buddha

Directed by: Vivek Ranjan Agnihotri
Produced by: Abhishek Agarwal, Pallavi Joshi and Vivek Ranjan Agnihotri 
Worldwide Release: Zee Studios
Music: Zee Music Co.
Starring: Mithun Chakraborty, Anupam Kher, Pallavi Joshi, Darshan Kumaar, Simratt Kaur

snippet.title: Rao Bahadur | Teaser | Satya Dev | Venkatesh Maha | GMB | SriChakraas | A+S | Summer 2026
snippet.description:
Rao Bahadur is a psychological drama set against the backdrop of a fading aristocracy - Made in Telugu, for the world.
 
Directed by acclaimed filmmaker Venkatesh Maha and starring the versatile Satya Dev as Rao Bahadur, the film is presented by Superstar Mahesh Babu & Namrata Shirodkar’s GMB Entertainment and produced by A+S Movies and SriChakraas Entertainments.
 
Releasing Summer 2026, in Theaters worldwide.
 
Genre - Psychological Drama, Suspense, Dark Comedy, Magical Realism.
 
 
Cast and Crew Details:
 
Cast - Satya Dev, Vikas Muppala, Deepa Thomas, Bala Parasar, Anand Bharathi, Pranay Vaka, Kunal Kaushik, Master Kiran and others.

About YRF Spy Universe:
YRF Spy Universe is a first of its kind cinematic universe of spy thriller films in India. The first film in the universe, "Ek Tha Tiger," starring Salman Khan and Katrina Kaif was released in 2012, followed by its sequel "Tiger Zinda Hai" in 2017. The third film in the universe, "War" was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. "Pathaan" was the fourth instalment in the Spy Universe franchise which was released in 2023 starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham. "Tiger 3", the fifth instalment in the YRF Spy Universe and the third film in the Tiger series, starring Salman Khan, Katrina Kaif and Emraan Hashmi, released in 2023. "War 2", the sixth film in the YRF Spy Universe, starring Hrithik Roshan, NTR and Kiara Advani, directed by Ayan Mukerji, released on 14 August 2025. "Alpha", the seventh film in the franchise and Hindi cinema’s first female-led YRF Spy Universe film, starring Alia Bhatt and Sharvari, will release on 25 December 2025.

इस गाने के सभी कॉपीराइट Trimurti Music World के पास सुरक्षित हैं। कोई भी व्यक्ति या चैनल इस गाने को बिना अनुमति के अपने प्लेटफॉर्म पर री-अपलोड न करे।

snippet.description:
SHANKARA (Official Video) I Pawan Singh I Kingstuff I Ganesh Acharya I Ullumanati IMahadev Song 2025 #pawansingh #mahadev #pawansinghnewsong #shiv 

 
🔥 “Shankara” The New Age Mahadev Anthem is here! Experience the power, devotion, and energy like never before with Power Star Pawan Singh in this electrifying musical journey, directed and choreographed by Bollywood legend Ganesh Acharya.
 
OUT NOW – Witness the magic before the full release!

👉 Don’t forget to LIKE, COMMENT, SHARE & SUBSCRIBE for more Mahadev songs, Bhojpuri hits, and power-packed performances by Pawan Singh.
 
⸻
 
🎵 Song Credits
 
Audio

🎤 Singer : Power Star Pawan Singh
🎤 Rap: Kingstuff
🎼 Music & Lyrics: Ullumanati
🎼 Mix Master : Amit Monga

 
Video
Cast: Power Star Pawan Singh
Director & Choreographer: Ganesh Acharya
DOP: Ajay Pandey
Editor: Manoj Magar
Online Editor : Sayan Mal
Colorist : R P Singh
VFX : 4K Visuals 
Costumes : Jayshree 
Line Production : Monty Productions 
 
⸻
 
Produced by: Rashmi Devi Films Productions Pvt. Ltd.
Digital Partner: Global Music Junction Pvt. Ltd.
Promotions: RD Music & Records Team
Poster Design: Aman Kalsi
 
⸻

Lyrics : 

Bina tere ye kut halahal
Kaun hai peene wala re
Kal kut ka kare varan wo
Kaun hai jeene wala re
Bhal chandra bole bhandari 
Aan padi hai vipda bhari
Kasht niware kaun humaro
Surpati aye sharan tihari

Kal garal ye kanth ramaye vastu digambara shankara


Shankara Shankara
Vishambhara 
Shankara


bethe dhyaan magan bje dadum dum dum damru tera
bethe atal atari bhole ka kailash pe dera
vipda padi asur Gano pe sbne tera naam pukara
bachalo mahade sb dekhen ab rasta tera
pee gye bhole vish ka payala 
dhehke ab kanth mein jawala
gal neela padne lga toh
Gora maiyan ne smbhala
bethe fr dhyaan m bhole
har koi har har bole
gunje fr naam tera jai jai ho
vishambhraaaaaaa


Tere gale mai jo mala bhujango ki
Saje hai kanth mai visdhar bada
(Tere gale mai samaya jo pyala ye
Jawala ka na se bhayankar sada) x2

(Bane sanghni aadi teri 
Anhad naad samadi teri
Teen bhuwan mai kaun hai duja 
Kate hai jissay vyadi meri) x2

Bhujunga bhusan dhyan dharo re ab to maheswara


shankara Shankara
Visambhara
shankara

snippet.title: #Video | Najariya Najar Se |Godfather | #Khesari Lal Yadav |#Priyanka Singh |New Bhojpuri Song 2025
snippet.description:
"Najariya Najar Se" is the latest romantic Bhojpuri song of 2025, released under Times Music Bhojpuri from the upcoming movie "Godfather." Sung by the dynamic duo Khesari Lal Yadav and Priyanka Singh, this love track beautifully captures the essence of romance through heartfelt lyrics and soulful melodies. With its catchy composition and visually stunning official video, the song is quickly becoming a fan favorite across social media and music platforms.

The music video showcases a compelling love story blending traditional Bhojpuri vibes with a modern cinematic touch. Whether you're a fan of Bhojpuri cinema, love songs, or the chart-topping voice of Khesari Lal Yadav, "Najariya Najar Se" is a must-watch and a must-listen.

snippet.title: #Video | पित्तल के दाना | Pittal Ke Dana | Raushan Rohi New Song | Tanya Tiwari  | New Bhojpuri Song
snippet.description:
"पित्तल के दाना" एक नया और जोशीला भोजपुरी गीत है, जिसे रौशन रोही ने अपनी दमदार आवाज़ में गाया है और तान्या तिवारी ने शानदार अदाओं से सजाया है। इस गाने में देसी मिज़ाज, धमाकेदार बीट्स और मनोरंजन का भरपूर तड़का है, जो इसे सुनने और देखने वालों को झूमने पर मजबूर कर देता है।

Subscribe to our channel for more Bhojpuri Songs:
https://youtube.com/c/SaregamaHumBhojpuri

Credits:-

Song Name - Pittal Ke Dana
Hindi - पित्तल के दाना
Singer - Raushan Rohi
Featuring - Tanya Tiwari 
Music - Pappu Bhai
Lyrics - Raja Roshan 
Composer - Roshan Rohi
Mix & Master - Ankit Ahir
Director - Pawan Pathak 
Choreographer -Sahil Raj
Dop - Rahul Yadav
Editor - Rohan 
Di - Rohit Singh

Lyrics:-

F अरे हमर फेरा में केतना हो गेलै राजा से रंक,
अब तू ऐन बजावे रंगदारी वाला शंख।
अरे भले डरो हकौ तोरा से पूलिस थाना रे,
M जे रेट में किनोही तू सोना के खजाना गे,
उ रेट में किनोही हम पित्तल के दाना गे।

अंतरा 1
F अरे तोरा जैसन ढेरे हम देखलिऐ गुंडा रंगदार,
हमरा न बतावे रे छौड़ा कि केतना में आवै हथियार।
अरे जूटो होतौ ढंग से न घर के खर्ची खाना रे,
M जे रेट में किनोही तू सोना के खजाना गे,
उ रेट में किनोही हम पित्तल के दाना गे।

अंतरा 2
F अरे जवन कमवा करो ही उहे करो है हमर खनदान,
जेतना नय तोरा होतौ रे छौड़ा ओतना है हमर पहचान।
अरे राजा रौशन रोहिया तू त लागो ही निकामा रे,
M जे रेट में किनोही तू सोना के खजाना गे,
उ रेट में किनोही हम पित्तल के दाना गे।

 ಸ್ವೀಟಾದ shock-u

snippet.title: Rippan Swaamy Official Trailer | Vijay Raghavendra | Ashwini Chandrashekar | Kishor Mudubidire | PRK
snippet.description:
Panchaanana Films productions in association with PRK Audio
presents
Rippan Swaamy - A rural thriller set in the fictional Malnad village of Snana Kopa.
The story unfolds after the mysterious suicide of Rippan Swaamy, leading to a trail of secrets, drama, and suspense. As the mystery deepens, the truth behind his name and death slowly unravels.

The film is set to release in theatres on August 29.
 🎵 Listen to the soulful songs exclusively on PRK Audio.

Production House: Panchaanana Films
Directed by: Kishor Mudubidire
Produced by: Panchaanana Films

Cast: Vijay Raghavendra, Ashwini Chandrashekar, Prakash Thuminadu, Vajradheer Jain, Yamuna Srinidhi, Krishnamurthy Kavattaru, Santhosh Shetty

snippet.title: Sekiro: No Defeat | Official Trailer | Crunchyroll
snippet.description:
Sekiro: No Defeat is coming exclusively to Crunchyroll!

The time is Sengoku.

Japan is fractured into many independent nations entangled in ceaseless war. At the center lies Ashina, a land of sacred earth and ancient mystery. Two decades after Sword Saint Isshin Ashina reclaimed the region in a brutal coup, a new threat emerges from within: The Interior Ministry. Desperate to protect his homeland, Isshin’s grandson Genichiro turns to forbidden powers. The only hope lies in a kidnapped boy — the Divine Heir — and his silent protector: a loyal shinobi known only as Sekiro.

This is the story of a lord and his retainer — and their quest to restore balance to a nation on the edge.

Crunchyroll brings you the latest clips, openings, full episodes, and more from your favorite anime!

snippet.title: When And Where : Yo Yo Honey Singh | Shehnaaz Gill | Ikk Kudi | New Punjabi Song 2025
snippet.description:
Get ready to vibe to the hottest track of the season! 🌟 Presenting “When and Where”, a high-energy, visually striking banger from the upcoming Punjabi film Ikk Kudi, starring and produced by the stunning Shehnaaz Gill and featuring the iconic Yo Yo Honey Singh.

🔥 Watch the sizzling chemistry, bold Jamaican-inspired visuals, and feel the pulse of the beat that’s taking over every dance floor!

Hawavan rehndi badal diyan
Ruttan russiyan tu na manniyan
Kade mai na manneya
Manavegi tah mann javange
Mann javange
Begani unjh lakh laddian teri adiyan
Mitran de hathe chadiyan
Khand pariyan 
Veke hauli hathi khavange, hathi khavange
Ni dass tenu kithe milna kiven milna
Kiddan kinne bajje kide vehde milna
Ni nangey pairi bhajji avanage
Tenu morh khare labbi javange
Ni dass tenu kithe milna kiven milna
Kiddan kinne bajje kide vehde milna
Ni nangey pairi bhajji avanage
Tenu morh khare labbi javange
Nattiyan rakhdi kokey rakhdi
Teeh saalan di munda chali
Pakkhiyan vargi hasse khandi
Dhee chavan di dhuppa kardi
Mauke labdhi hauke labhdi
Mainu buhaa dho ke labhdi
Gal di gani kho ke labhdi
Soni lagdhi rondi hasdi
Ni akkahn jiven phulljhadian, Haale ladiyan
Pariyan teh phul kallian tethon sadian
Laggian teh luk javange, Luk javange
Ni dass tenu kithe milna kiven milna
Kiddan kinne bajje kide vehde milna
Ni nangey pairi bhajji avanage
Tenu morh khare labbi javange
Ni dass tenu kithe milna kiven milna
Kiddan kinne bajje kide vehde milna
Ni nangey pairi bhajji avanage
Tenu morh khare labbi javange
Kehndi yo yo honey singh
Ikk kudi

About T-Series Fox 

On our channel we create а trailer mashups ▷
Also known as recut trailers, involve collecting multiple pieces of film footage from one or multiple movies and Add Our Own Dialogues To Make A New And Fresh Story, editing them to create a new trailer. Trailer mashups are often created for a movie that does not exist now or to change the genre of an existing film. These are derivative works as defined by the United States Copyright Act 17 U.S.C. § 101, and as such, may find protection from copyright claims under the doctrine of fair use.

The trailer mashups are not only a user generated form of digital creativity but a way to create anticipation for future releases, working in tandem with current movie trailers. Movie trailers are designed to give minimal plot detail and to create hype and anticipation. Fan made trailer mashups allow the audience to perform their own cinematic spin on current movie footage. This allows the trailer to focus on a specific actor or portion of the film. It could even change the plot ocr genre of the film entirely.

This video is a parody DUE to its derivative/ transformative nature this video is covered as a Fair Use of material.

snippet.title: Dashavatar Trailer: कोकणातली दशावताराची परंपरा ते राखणदार, महाराष्ट्राचा दशावतार साऊथला टक्कर देणार?
snippet.description:
#BolBhidu #Dashavatar #DilipPrabhavalkar

स्क्रीनवर दिसणारी, जमिनीवर ठेवलेली एक दगडी मूर्ती, बाजूला लावलेला दिवा.. हातातली काठी टेकवत चालणारी पण अंधुक दिसणारी एक व्यक्ती आणि कानावर पडणारे शब्द, राखणदारा पुढं कोण मोठो न्हाय. दशावतार या मराठी पिक्चरच्या ट्रेलरमध्ये दिसणारं हे दृश्य. जे अंगावर सरसरून काटा आणतं आणि मनात एक उत्सुकता कायम राहते, राखणदार म्हणजे कोण ? पण ट्रेलरच्या सुरुवातीला आणि शेवटी आपल्या डोक्यात राखणदार नसतो, आपल्या डोक्यात दशावतार असतो. कोकणातली समृद्ध परंपरा दाखवणारा, शेकडो वर्षांचा वारसा जपणारा दशावतार. पिक्चरच्या नावापासून ते दृष्यांपर्यंत विषय दशावताराभोवती फिरत असला, तरी ट्रेलर बघून अंदाज येतो की मूळ विषय राखणदाराचा आहे आणि कोकणातल्या जमिनी आणि जंगलांचाही. कारण यातच डायलॉग आहे, जंगल आपल्या बापाचं आहे. पण राखणदार म्हणजे नेमका कोण ? कोकणात राखणदाराला इतकं महत्त्व का आहे ? आणि दशावतारमुळे महाराष्ट्राला आपला कांतारा मिळाला आहे, असं का म्हणता येतंय ? पाहुयात या व्हिडीओमधून.

Check out CottonKing - Men's Cotton Wear: https://cottonking.com/?srsltid=AfmBO...

snippet.title: Smriti Phatoley | স্মৃতি ফাটলে | Dhumketu | Dev | Subhashree | Nachiketa Chakraborty | Anupam Roy
snippet.description:
নতুন বাংলা ছবি ধূমকেতু থেকে মন ছুঁয়ে যাওয়া গান “স্মৃতি ফাটলে”। নচিকেতার অনবদ্য কণ্ঠে, অনুপম রায়ের সুর ও কথায় এই গান প্রেম, আবেগ আর স্মৃতির এক অনন্য কাব্যিক যাত্রা। দেব ও শুভশ্রীর অসাধারণ অভিনয় এই গানকে করে তুলেছে আরও হৃদয়স্পর্শী।

Presenting the soulful new Bengali movie song – Smriti Phatoley. Sung by the legendary Nachiketa Chakraborty, this heartfelt track is composed and written by the exceptionally talented Anupam Roy. Featuring the dynamic duo Dev and Subhashree, the song beautifully blends melody and emotion, making it one of the most memorable highlights from the Bengali movie Dhumketu.

snippet.title: Woh jo mujhko dekh ke hanse Paana chaahoon raat din jise (Lyrics) Ajj Din Chadheya - Pritam & Rahat
snippet.description:
🎶 Woh jo mujhko dekh ke hanse Paana chaahoon raat din jise (Lyrics) Ajj Din Chadheya - Pritam & Rahat Fateh Ali Khan

👉 Follow Pritam:
https://www.instagram.com/ipritamofficial
https://www.facebook.com/Pritam

👉 Follow Rahat Fateh Ali Khan
https://www.instagram.com/officialrfakworld
https://www.facebook.com/RFAKWorld
https://twitter.com/rfakworld

🎤 Lyrics:

Ajj din chadheya tere rang warga
Ajj din chadheya tere rang warga
Phool sa hai khila aaj din

Rabba, mere din yeh na dhale
Woh jo mujhe khwaab mein mile
Usey tu laga de ab gale
Tainu dil da vaasta

Rabba, aaya dar pe yaar ke
Saara jahaan chhod-chhaad ke
Mere sapne sanwaar de
Tainu dil da vaasta

Ajj din chadheya tere rang warga

Bakhsha gunaahon ko, sun ke duaaon ko
Rabba, pyaar hai tune sab ko hi de diya
Meri bhi aahon ko, sun le duaaon ko
Mujhko woh dila maine jisko hai dil diya

Oh, bakhsha gunaahon ko, sun ke duaaon ko
Rabba, pyaar hai tune sab ko hi de diya
Meri bhi aahon ko, sun le duaaon ko
Mujhko woh dila maine jisko hai dil diya

Aas woh, pyaas woh, uske de itna bata

snippet.title: Vilen - Restart (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
Restart is not just about love lost — it’s about rediscovering yourself when everything around you feels broken. It’s about learning that your true ‘everything’ has always been within you. This song is a reminder that endings are not final; they are opportunities to rebuild, to grow, and to begin again. To Restart.

snippet.title: Franklin & Shinchan vs The Dog Mafia! 🐶🚔 | GTA 5 Malayalam Police Story Part 2
snippet.description:
Franklin and Shinchan are back in Part 2 of our GTA 5 Malayalam Police Story! 🔥
After Chop gets kidnapped, Franklin takes a goon hostage to find the truth. But things get out of hand when a new villain Butcher is revealed — a dangerous man who runs a dog smuggling company called Butcher & Co. 🐕✈️

Shinchan accidentally discovers Chop trapped among many other dogs in cages. With time running out, Franklin and Shinchan rush to the airport to stop Butcher from smuggling the dogs to China. Will they save Chop in time? Watch till the end for the epic airport combat and rescue mission! 💥🐾

👉 Don’t forget to Like 👍, Share ❤️, and Subscribe 🔔 to The Mallu Don for more funny GTA 5 Malayalam story videos featuring Franklin, Shinchan, Shiranui, and more!

सुन्दरकांड” – श्री राम चरित मानस का 5 वा अध्याय/कांड है। सुन्दर कांड (Sundar Kand) को सबसे पहले रामायण में श्री वाल्मीकि जी ने संस्कृत में लिखा था। बाद में तुलसी दस जी ने जब श्री राम चरित मानस लिखी, तो सुन्दर कांड का अवधी भाषा वाला रूप हम सब के सामने आया 
सुन्दरकाण्ड में हनुमान जी का सीता माता को खोजने के लिए की गयी लंका यात्रा का सम्पूर्ण मनमोहक बखान किया गया है।
सुन्दरकांड एक ऐसा भाग है जो सिर्फ हनुमान जी की वीरता का बखान करता है । सुन्दर कांड हनुमान जी पर केंद्रित सबसे पुरानी रचना है। ऐसा माना जाता है के सुन्दरकाण्ड के पाठ से सभी मनोकामनाएं पूर्ण होती हैं ।

सुन्दर कांड के फायदे | Benefits of - Sunder Kand
 यह कहा जाता है कि चालीस सप्ताह तक लगातार जो कोई श्रद्धापूर्वक Sundarkand का पाठ करता है, तो उसके सभी मनोरथ पूरे होते हैं तथा जीवन के सभी कष्ट, दुःख, परेशानियाँ दूर हो जाती हैँ । कई ज्योतिषी भी विपरित परिस्थितियों में सुंदरकांड करने की ही सलाह देते हैं। यदि किसी व्यक्ति के जीवन में अत्यधिक परेशानियां हो तथा कोई काम नहीं बन पा रहा है, आत्मविश्वास की कमी हो तो सुंदरकांड के पाठ से शुभ फल प्राप्त होता है।

सुन्दरकांड एक ऐसा भाग है जो सिर्फ हनुमान जी की वीरता का बखान करता है । सुन्दर कांड हनुमान जी पर केंद्रित सबसे पुरानी रचना है। ऐसा माना जाता है के सुन्दरकाण्ड के पाठ से सभी मनोकामनाएं पूर्ण होती हैं ।

सुन्दर कांड के फायदे | Benefits of - Sunder Kand
 यह कहा जाता है कि चालीस सप्ताह तक लगातार जो कोई श्रद्धापूर्वक Sundarkand का पाठ करता है, तो उसके सभी मनोरथ पूरे होते हैं तथा जीवन के सभी कष्ट, दुःख, परेशानियाँ दूर हो जाती हैँ । कई ज्योतिषी भी विपरित परिस्थितियों में सुंदरकांड करने की ही सलाह देते हैं। यदि किसी व्यक्ति के जीवन में अत्यधिक परेशानियां हो तथा कोई काम नहीं बन पा रहा है, आत्मविश्वास की कमी हो तो सुंदरकांड के पाठ से शुभ फल प्राप्त होता है।
